Entries.default: "That Dawnstar may be able to help. What say?"
"Help how, poison me? Ekera, no thanks."
"You hear? The Dawnstars granted Pitli the power to heal the plagued folk."
"Surely, so you got the pustule drained?"
"It was only a matter of time before they got caught and sent to the Old City."
"The Mataru came for them? I pity their fate."
"I always knew she was a blessing on us. Never doubted her."
